ActRoyal Canadian Mint Act
PrecisAppointment of FIONA L. MACDONALD of Vancouver, British Columbia, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Royal Canadian Mint, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Susan Dujmovic, whose term has expired.
